{"html":"<section>\n\t\t\t<h2>Tunes Played by the Chimes of St. Sepulchre’s Church at Cullerne</h2>\n\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>At 3 o’clock.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>New Sabbath</span>\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"A score for the Long Metre (8.8.8.8) hymn tune “New Sabbath” in D, scored in SATB for chimes in ³⁄₂ time.\" src=\"../images/illustration-2.svg\"/>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>At 6 o’clock.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Bermondsey</span>\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"A score for the hymn tune “Bermondsey” in D, scored in SATB for chimes in ³⁄₂ time; it has a metre of 664.664.4464.\" src=\"../images/illustration-3.svg\"/>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>At 9 o’clock.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Sheldon</span>\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"A score for the Common Metre (8.6.8.6) hymn tune “Sheldon” in D, scored in SATB for chimes in ³⁄₂ time.\" src=\"../images/illustration-4.svg\"/>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>At 12 o’clock.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Mount Ephraim</span>\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"A score for the Short Metre (6.6.8.6) hymn tune “Mount Ephraim” in D, scored in SATB for chimes in ³⁄₂ time.\" src=\"../images/illustration-5.svg\"/>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t</section>"}